<p>Cocoon above! Cocoon below!<br>
Stealthy Cocoon, why hide you so<br>
What all the world suspect?<br>
An hour, and gay on every tree<br>
Your secret, perched in ecstasy<br>
Defies imprisonment!<br>
<br>
An hour in Chrysalis to pass,<br>
Then gay above receding grass<br>
A Butterfly to go!<br>
A moment to interrogate,<br>
Then wiser than a "Surrogate,"<br>
The Universe to know!</p>